@MarketHub.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5067

### Get all events
GET {{MarketHub.Api_HostAddress}}/api/events
Accept: application/json

### Create new event
POST {{MarketHub.Api_HostAddress}}/api/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Big Yard Sale in West Valley",
  "description": "Furniture, clothes, and electronics",
  "category": "yard_sale",
  "address": "123 Main St, West Valley City, UT 84119",
